<div type="description" n="monument">
<head>Description of Monument</head>
<p>Two fragments from the lower part of a <rs type="material" key="marmor">white marble</rs> <rs type="objectType" reg="base">base</rs> with moulded panels on four sides. a: right side fragment (<measure dim="width" type="length" unit="metre">0.28</measure> ×<measure dim="height" type="length" unit="metre"> 0.58</measure> ×<measure dim="depth" type="length" unit="metre"> 0.25</measure>) with moulding to right. b: lower left corner fragment, with moulding to left and below (<measure dim="width" type="length" unit="metre">0.25</measure> × <measure dim="height" type="length" unit="metre">0.34</measure> × <measure dim="depth" type="length" unit="metre">0.34</measure>).</p>
</div>

<div type="description" n="text">
<head>Description of Text</head>
<p><rs type="execution" key="scalpro">Inscribed</rs> on the face. a. inscribed face <measure dim="width" type="length" unit="metre">0.19</measure> ×<measure dim="height" type="length" unit="metre"> 0.45</measure>; b. inscribed face <measure dim="width" type="length" unit="metre">0.17</measure> × <measure dim="height" type="length" unit="metre">0.39</measure>.</p>
</div>

<div type="description" n="letters">
<head>Description of Letters</head>
<p><measure dim="height" type="length" unit="metre">0.02</measure>; ligatures: ΤΗ l.14, ΗΝ l.20; the numerals at the end of l. 17 cut on moulding.</p>
</div>

